  "description": "Use this skill when defining AI governance policies, designing human oversight workflows, documenting bias mitigation strategies, or meeting regulatory transparency requirements for Salesforce AI features. Trigger keywords: responsible AI, AI bias, AI audit trail, AI transparency, human-in-the-loop, AI risk inventory, AI disclosure. NOT for Trust Layer technical configuration \u2014 that is covered by agentforce/einstein-trust-layer.",
  "file_location": "skills/admin/ai-ethics-and-governance-requirements",
  "id": "admin/ai-ethics-and-governance-requirements",
  "inputs": [
    "List of AI features or Agentforce agents currently deployed or planned in the org",
    "Applicable regulatory or compliance frameworks (e.g., EU AI Act, CCPA, HIPAA)",
    "Current data residency and retention constraints",
    "Org profile: industry, customer-facing vs. internal use cases, data sensitivity level"
  ],
  "name": "ai-ethics-and-governance-requirements",
